         <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint${sound:npc_Gereint_2902_qu_17.ogg}<BR>We did our best...<BR>You don't need to blame yourself and you shouldn't.<BR>You did your best, Argenta….</html>]]></talk_question>
