         <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Geraint${action:Talk}<BR>I can't see….<BR>I was hit directly by the Black Dragon's breath so it would be hard for me to restore my eyesight now….</html>]]></talk_question>
      </talk_paragraph>
      <talk_paragraph index="006" image="QN_Npc_Geraint_Closeeye.dds" itemindex="">
